<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>6318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>9317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，天气很晴朗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个农夫和他的儿子牵着驴子向集市走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们打算在集市里卖掉那头驴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走着走着，遇到了几名游客。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看那儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们有一头驴却不骑。哈哈！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>真是没用的驴呀！”其中一个人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊，主人也很蠢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个人大笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>听了他们的话，父亲感到非常难过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他让儿子骑在驴上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“儿子，骑到驴上去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他们经过了一位老妇人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她坐在路边的椅子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个儿子真不孝。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他让自己的父亲走路，自己却骑在驴上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“儿子，从驴上下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我骑上去更好一点儿。”父亲说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>父亲骑在驴上，儿子在旁边走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久，他们遇到了两位女士。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看看他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个父亲一定不是个好父亲。”一位女士说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。看看那个男孩儿多累啊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的儿子才应该骑在驴上。”另一位女士说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“儿子，我们一起骑在驴上吧。”父亲说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和儿子一起骑上了驴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他们遇到了两位男士。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太残忍了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看看他们如何对待那头可怜的驴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊，那头驴怎么能够同时载两个人呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它看起来一点儿力气都没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可怜的驴呀！”两人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>父亲和儿子看着驴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的驴看起来确实有点儿累啊。”父亲说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们该怎么办呢？”儿子问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们把驴扛在肩膀上吧。”父亲说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把驴的前腿和后腿分别拴在一起，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后把驴扛在了肩膀上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们过桥的时候，一些人看到他们，大笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦，哈哈！看啊！哈哈哈！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>多么可笑的两个人啊！哎呦，天啊!”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们笑得太大声，把驴吓到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>驴不停地摆动着腿，挣脱了他们的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>驴掉到河里，淹死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，我们的驴死了！”父亲大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回家的路上，父亲轻声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“儿子，当你试着取悦所有人的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后却谁也取悦不了啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>